    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "rt27",
      "x": 1630,
      "y": 920,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 135,
      "text": "HEART CHAMBERS\nRIGHT SIDE:\n• RA: receives deoxy blood (via vena cava)\n• RV: pumps to lungs (via pulmonary artery)\nLEFT SIDE:\n• LA: receives oxy blood (via pulm. veins)\n• LV: pumps to body (via aorta) - wall 3× thicker",
      "originalText": "HEART CHAMBERS\nRIGHT SIDE:\n• RA: receives deoxy blood (via vena cava)\n• RV: pumps to lungs (via pulmonary artery)\nLEFT SIDE:\n• LA: receives oxy blood (via pulm. veins)\n• LV: pumps to body (via aorta) - wall 3× thicker",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
