      "x": 2230,
      "y": 920,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 135,
      "text": "HEART VALVES\n• Tricuspid: RA↔RV\n  (3 flaps)\n• Bicuspid / Mitral:\n  LA↔LV (2 cusps)\n• Semilunar: at aorta\n  & pulmonary artery",
      "originalText": "HEART VALVES\n• Tricuspid: RA↔RV\n  (3 flaps)\n• Bicuspid / Mitral:\n  LA↔LV (2 cusps)\n• Semilunar: at aorta\n  & pulmonary artery",
